&lt;h2 id="-http-protocol">ðŸŒ HTTP Protocol
&lt;/h2>&lt;p>HTTP (&lt;strong>Hypertext Transfer Protocol&lt;/strong>) is a data transmission protocol on the web following a &lt;strong>request-response&lt;/strong> model.&lt;/p>
&lt;h3 id="-example-sending-http-requests-with-curl">ðŸ”¹ Example sending HTTP requests with cURL:
&lt;/h3>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;div class="chroma">
